Dim PreviousNumKP As Double Dim PreviousNumKI As Double Dim PreviousNumKD As Double Dim Enable As Boolean
'Private Sub BtnAuto_Released() ' On Error GoTo ErrHandler ' Application.ExecuteCommand ("REMARK AutoMan+" & Me.TagParameters(1) & "+Manual+Auto") 'Exit Sub 'ErrHandler: ' Application.LogDiagnosticsMessage "Falha ao registrar mudança para manual do PID: " & Me.TagParameters(1) ' Resume Next 'End Sub
'Private Sub BtnManual_Released() ' On Error GoTo ErrHandler ' Application.ExecuteCommand ("REMARK AutoMan+" & Me.TagParameters(1) & "+Auto+Manual") 'Exit Sub 'ErrHandler: ' Application.LogDiagnosticsMessage "Falha ao registrar mudança para manual do PID: " & Me.TagParameters(1) ' Resume Next 'End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String
INSTRUMENTO = Text1.Caption PONTEIRO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1)
If PONTEIRO_1 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) PONTEIRO_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 12, 1) If PONTEIRO_2 <> "-" Then INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5, 8) Else INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5, 7) + "_" + Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 13, 3) End If Else INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) PONTEIRO_3 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 13, 1) If PONTEIRO_3 <> "-" Then INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6, 8) Else INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6, 7) + "_" + Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 14, 3) End If End If
If INSTR_TIPO = "L" Then AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "' And (EventSource LIKE 'H_' Or EventSource LIKE 'L_')" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%LA%H_%' Or SourceName LIKE '%LA%L_%')" Else AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "'" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO & "%'" End If
End Sub
Private Sub NumKP_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer) On Error GoTo ErrHandler If KeyCode = 13 Then If Enable Then Application.ExecuteCommand ("REMARK KP+" & Me.TagParameters(1) & "+" & PreviousNumKP & "+" & Me.NumKP.Value) ' & "+ $" & Me.TagParameters(1) & ".auto$") PreviousNumKP = NumKP.Value End If End If Exit Sub ErrHandler: Application.LogDiagnosticsMessage "Falha ao registrar mudança no KP do PID: " & Me.TagParameters(1) Resume Next End Sub
Private Sub NumKP_GotFocus() On Error GoTo ErrHandler Enable = True PreviousNumKP = NumKP.Value Exit Sub ErrHandler: PreviousNumKP = 0 Resume Next End Sub
Private Sub NumKI_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer) On Error GoTo ErrHandler If KeyCode = 13 Then If Enable Then Application.ExecuteCommand ("REMARK KI+" & Me.TagParameters(1) & "+" & PreviousNumKI & "+" & Me.NumKI.Value) ' & "+ $" & Me.TagParameters(1) & ".auto$") PreviousNumKI = NumKI.Value End If End If Exit Sub ErrHandler: Application.LogDiagnosticsMessage "Falha ao registrar mudança no KI do PID: " & Me.TagParameters(1) Resume Next End Sub
Private Sub NumKI_GotFocus() On Error GoTo ErrHandler Enable = True PreviousNumKI = NumKI.Value Exit Sub ErrHandler: PreviousNumKI = 0 Resume Next End Sub
